title: Suruchi
description: Vegetarian Indian restaurant located inside hotel Swati. Features Gujarati, Rajasthani, Jain, Bombay specialty, and north Indian thali. No alcohol served. The kamandal (in which they put the food to serve to their customers) carried by the waiters makes the place look like a typical Gujrati house. Sitting capacity of 70 people, Suruchi covers an area of 1600 sq feet.
